That is: Any potential buyer of Sculptor (Rithm, Weinstein, the anonymous =
=E2=80=9CBidder D=E2=80=9D who walked away from Sculptor earlier in its sal=
e process) will prefer to have Och=E2=80=99s support, or at least grudging =
