t was mostly (1) revenge on Jimmy Levin and (2) Och=E2=80=99s own tax inter=
ests.
Specifically:
=09The tax receivable agreement, or TRA: Some companies have TRAs that acce=
lerate on a change of control, so that, instead of paying out the tax benef=
its over years as the company realizes taxable income, they just pay a big =
lump sum when the merger happens. Sculptor=E2=80=99s TRA doesn=E2=80=99t do=
