itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"c=
olor: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; =
border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color:=
 #ccc;">  have</a> <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click=
/32559282.261426/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLz=
IwMjMtMDgtMjEvZXZlcnlvbmUtd2FudHMtYS1waWVjZS1vZi1zY3VscHRvcj9jbXBpZD1CQkQwO=
